-- Bruce Discusses New Fed Documentary ‘Money for Nothing’ (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-09-17T20:02:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-17/bruce-discusses-new-fed-documentary-money-for-nothing-audio-.html
Jim Bruce, movie editor and 
documentary producer, discusses how he came up with the idea for
his new documentary, "Money for Nothing: Inside the Federal 
Reserve," how he funded it, and how he convinced top current and
former Fed officials to be part of it.  Bruce speaks with 
Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's 
"The Hays Advantage."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 18:50
 